@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<section class="about-us container py-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"] – BuzzAir</h2>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <p>
                At <strong>BuzzAir</strong>, we believe travel should be more than just getting from A to B—it’s about the memories you make along the way. As one of the world’s fastest-growing airlines, we’re proud to connect you to over 200 destinations across six continents, helping you discover new cultures, cuisines, and experiences.
            </p>

            <p>
                Our commitment to your comfort and safety is at the heart of everything we do. From our industry-leading on-board services—complimentary gourmet meals, spacious seating, and award-winning entertainment—to our dedicated customer care team, every detail is designed to make your journey relaxing, seamless, and enjoyable.
            </p>

            <p>
                We’ve invested in the latest fuel-efficient aircraft and partnered with global sustainability initiatives to reduce our environmental footprint. Because we know that a truly responsible airline looks after both its passengers and the planet.
            </p>

            <p>
                Whether you’re flying for business, family, or the adventure of a lifetime, you’ll find our friendly crew ready to welcome you onboard, and our loyalty program rewards every mile you travel with exclusive perks and upgrades.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-4 text-center fst-italic">
                “Your journey is our passion—thank you for choosing BuzzAir.”
            </p>

            <p class="text-end fw-bold">
                With warm regards,<br />
                The BuzzAir Team
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
